ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:01:00.000Z","msg":"下回合就反cup你班疤泥狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9591b9c71b6d08f307b6e2ab407ef3a63809202","tid":1019390,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:04:53.000Z","msg":"曼聯唔使為英超冠軍而煩惱，可集中力量力爭歐聯 爭緊前4架..."},{"pid":"71232ef3f0521f08faf2c12d055bb69a15d7e927","tid":1019390,"uid":100766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:10:44.000Z","msg":"呢啲垃圾文都出到街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896e02c17dc9f7e2b04ade405e4ae99d56d746f0","tid":1019390,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9591b9c71b6d08f307b6e2ab407ef3a63809202","tid":1019390,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:04:53.000Z","msg":"曼聯唔使為英超冠軍而煩惱，可集中力量力爭歐聯 爭緊前4架..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:12:33.000Z","msg":"拎歐聯冠軍 仲使爭四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5c7a55fc58cb28047083798380d5a9d550ee10","tid":1019390,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c12978fe1b00f599e373bb8349d6fe3a75be6bd","tid":1019390,"uid":119729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"896e02c17dc9f7e2b04ade405e4ae99d56d746f0","tid":1019390,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9591b9c71b6d08f307b6e2ab407ef3a63809202","tid":1019390,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:04:53.000Z","msg":"曼聯唔使為英超冠軍而煩惱，可集中力量力爭歐聯 爭緊前4架..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T03:12:33.000Z","msg":"拎歐聯冠軍 仲使爭四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201